description: Commercial ACID Compliant Object Database for WinRT and Windows Phone 8. Features include LINQ index queries, lazy loading, paging, transactions, constraints, triggers, caching, BLOB, CLOB, Import XML, Export XML, Auto Identity Primary Keys, foreign key relationships, AES encryption, and MiniLZO compression.
releaseNotes: Kellerman Software announces a minor update to Ninja WinRT Database.  Performance has been increased when inserting thousands of records with an index.  Stablity has been increased when the parent application crashes.
